convexpolygonarea module¶

convexpolygonarea.main() → None¶

Main function to read, process, and output the area of each convex polygon.

convexpolygonarea.parse_input() → List[Polygon]¶

Parses input from standard input according to the Kattis problem format.

Returns: List[Polygon]: A list of Polygon objects constructed from the input data.
